                    <section class="content-section" id="where-it-breaks">
                        <h2>Where Each Tool Breaks</h2>
                        <p><strong>Lemlist breaks</strong> when team size grows. At 5+ SDRs, the per-user cost ($495+/month) exceeds what most SMBs budget for cold email. The LinkedIn automation also carries account restriction risk from LinkedIn's ToS enforcement.</p>
                        <p><strong>Saleshandy breaks</strong> when personalization is the priority. It has no personalized image capability, no AI icebreaker generation, and no LinkedIn or phone automation. For campaigns targeting senior buyers who receive dozens of cold emails daily, Saleshandy's output blends in rather than standing out.</p>
